		"info_2v2_text": "In 2v2, the average Elo of the team is used. Both players on a team receive the same Elo change.",
		"info_example_title": "Example",
		"info_example_text": "Player A (1200 Elo) beats Player B (1300 Elo). Since A was the underdog, A gains about +20 points while B loses about -20. If B had won, the change would only be about +12/-12."
